      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines the "xml2rfc" version 2 vocabulary: an XML-based language used for writing RFCs and Internet-Drafts.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Version 2 represents the state of the vocabulary (as implemented by several tools and as used by the RFC Editor) around 2014.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This document obsoletes RFC 2629.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
